Meanwhile, Victoria is nominated for an Emmy, and Elkaâs suggestion that she fake a deadly disease to gain sympathy and votes requires her to play her most challenging role yet.

Love Is Blind

Victoria's daughter Emmy and Melanie's son Will break the news that they're engaged to each other, and Joy dates a 22-year-old who literally can't see her actual age.

Night at the Museum

In this Quickfire challenge, pop star Joe Jonas of the Jonas Brothers challenges the chefs to create a snack for children enjoying a sleepover at the American Museum of Natural History. For the Elimination challenge, the chefs cook breakfast inspired by a dinosaur's diet for the kids and their parents.

Mother Dearest

Adrianna has to un-invite Navid to her magazine premiere party after Victor arranges for her to go with Joe Jonas to boost her image.

Boyz II Dead

Geils and Tanner investigate the mysterious death of a reunited boy band member while Tribeca finally meets with Sgt. Pepper. Why? Seemingly, he's connected to Mayhem Global but what is Mayhem Global and why do they keep bringing it up?
